Wazuh Manager Configuration
Overview

This document describes the deployment and validation of the Wazuh Manager used as the central SIEM component in this lab. The manager is responsible for log ingestion, correlation, alerting, 
and visualization for all connected endpoints.

Environment

Operating System: Ubuntu Server

Role: Wazuh Manager, Indexer, and Dashboard (single-node)

Network: Internal / Host-only

Deployment Summary

The Wazuh Manager was installed using the official single-node installation method. All core services were deployed on the same host to support a controlled
lab environment while maintaining functional parity with enterprise deployments.

Service Validation

The following services were verified to be running successfully:

wazuh-manager
wazuh-indexer
wazuh-dashboard

Dashboard Access

The Wazuh Dashboard is accessible over HTTPS at:

https://<10.0.2.15>


Successful access confirms proper integration between the manager, indexer, and dashboard.

